### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Registrar usuário candidato
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "userType": "candidato",
  "candidateInfo": {
    "phone": "(11) 99999-9999"
  }
}

### Registrar usuário empresa
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TechCorp Ltda",
  "email": "contato@techcorp.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "userType": "empresa",
  "companyInfo": {
    "cnpj": "12.345.678/0001-90",
    "description": "Empresa de tecnologia",
    "sector": "Tecnologia"
  }
}

